<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Prediction Oversight ‚Äì Medisync Admin</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0066ff;
            --primary-dark: #0052cc;
            --secondary: #00d4aa;
            --secondary-dark: #00a8cc;
            --accent: #ff6b6b;
            --warning: #fbbf24;
            --danger: #ef4444;
            --success: #10b981;
            --dark: #1a1a2e;
            --light: #f8fafc;
            --gradient-hero: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066ff 0%, #00d4aa 50%, #667eea 100%);
            --gradient-admin: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 50%, #f093fb 100%);
            --gradient-danger: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 50%, #b91c1c 100%);
            --gradient-warning: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
            --gradient-info: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #6366f1 100%);
            --gradient-brain: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #a855f7 50%, #d946ef 100%);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Animated Background */
        .bg-animated {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #ee7752, #e73c7e, #23a6d5, #23d5ab);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientBG 15s ease infinite;
            opacity: 0.05;
        }

        @keyframes gradientBG {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        /* Navbar */
        .navbar-custom {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: var(--gradient-admin);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .btn-back {
            background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
            color: #667eea;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .btn-back:hover {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-logout {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            color: var(--danger);
            border: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-logout:hover {
            background: var(--danger);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Page Header */
        .page-header {
            background: var(--gradient-brain);
            padding: 3rem 0;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .page-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(50%, -50%);
        }

        .page-header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, 50%);
        }

        .page-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .page-header p {
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .brain-icon {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
        }

        /* Content Container */
        .content-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1.5rem 3rem;
        }

        /* Stats Cards */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .stat-card-header {
            padding: 1.25rem;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .stat-card-header.danger { background: var(--gradient-danger); }
        .stat-card-header.warning { background: var(--gradient-warning); }
        .stat-card-header.info { background: var(--gradient-info); }

        .stat-icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .stat-info h6 {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .stat-info h2 {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .stat-card-body {
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            background: white;
        }

        .stat-desc {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Table Card */
        .table-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .table-card-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #2d2d44 100%);
            padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .table-card-header h5 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .table-card-header .badge-count {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .custom-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .custom-table thead {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
        }

        .custom-table th {
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dark);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .custom-table td {
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .custom-table tbody tr {
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .custom-table tbody tr:hover {
            background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.03);
        }

        .patient-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--dark);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .patient-avatar {
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: var(--gradient-admin);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .medicine-name {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            color: #8b5cf6;
            padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.35rem;
        }

        .usage-badge {
            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
            color: #6366f1;
            padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .risk-badge {
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
        }

        .risk-badge.high {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
            color: #dc2626;
        }

        .risk-badge.warning {
            background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15);
            color: #d97706;
        }

        .risk-badge.info {
            background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
            color: #6366f1;
        }

        .empty-state {
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .empty-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--success);
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        }

        .empty-state h4 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .empty-state p {
            color: #64748b;
        }

        /* Info Card */
        .info-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05) 0%, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.05) 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
        }

        .info-card-header {
            background: var(--gradient-brain);
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .info-card-header h5 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .info-card-body {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .info-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .info-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 1rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
        }

        .info-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .info-list li i {
            color: #8b5cf6;
            margin-top: 3px;
        }

        .info-list li span {
            color: #475569;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .info-list li strong {
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        .risk-indicator {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.35rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .risk-indicator.high {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            color: #dc2626;
        }

        .risk-indicator.warning {
            background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
            color: #d97706;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .page-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .page-header h1 {
                font-size: 1.75rem;
            }

            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .custom-table th,
            .custom-table td {
                padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            }
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .stat-card, .table-card, .info-card {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
        }

        .stat-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .stat-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
        .stat-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-animated"></div>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar-custom">
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">üõ°Ô∏è Medisync Admin</a>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                <a href="/admin/dashboard" class="btn-back">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Dashboard
                </a>
                <form method="post" action="/admin/logout" class="d-inline m-0">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-logout">
                        <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Logout
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>
                <div class="brain-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                </div>
                Prediction System Oversight
            </h1>
            <p>Monitor medicine repetition alerts and AI-powered risk detection</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content-container">
        <!-- Stats Grid -->
        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-card-header danger">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-info">
                        <h6>High Risk Cases</h6>
                        <h2><%= predictions.filter(p => p.risk_level === 'HIGH RISK').length %></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card-body">
                    <div class="stat-desc">
                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                        6+ medicine uses detected
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-card-header warning">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-info">
                        <h6>Warning Cases</h6>
                        <h2><%= predictions.filter(p => p.risk_level === 'WARNING').length %></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card-body">
                    <div class="stat-desc">
                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                        4-5 medicine uses detected
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-card-header info">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-info">
                        <h6>Total Alerts</h6>
                        <h2><%= predictions.length %></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card-body">
                    <div class="stat-desc">
                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                        Active medicine repetitions
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Predictions Table -->
        <div class="table-card">
            <div class="table-card-header">
                <h5>
                    <i class="fas fa-pills"></i>
                    Medicine Repetition Alerts
                </h5>
                <span class="badge-count">Last 2 Months</span>
            </div>
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="custom-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th><i class="fas fa-user me-2"></i>Patient Name</th>
                            <th><i class="fas fa-capsules me-2"></i>Medicine Name</th>
                            <th><i class="fas fa-redo me-2"></i>Usage Count</th>
                            <th><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2"></i>Risk Level</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% if (predictions && predictions.length > 0) { %>
                            <% predictions.forEach(p => { %>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        <div class="patient-name">
                                            <div class="patient-avatar">
                                                <%= p.name ? p.name.charAt(0).toUpperCase() : 'P' %>
                                            </div>
                                            <%= p.name %>
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td>
                                        <span class="medicine-name">
                                            <i class="fas fa-pill"></i>
                                            <%= p.medicine_name %>
                                        </span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td>
                                        <span class="usage-badge"><%= p.usage_count %> times</span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td>
                                        <% if (p.risk_level === 'HIGH RISK') { %>
                                            <span class="risk-badge high">
                                                <i class="fas fa-circle"></i> HIGH RISK
                                            </span>
                                        <% } else if (p.risk_level === 'WARNING') { %>
                                            <span class="risk-badge warning">
                                                <i class="fas fa-circle"></i> WARNING
                                            </span>
                                        <% } else { %>
                                            <span class="risk-badge info">
                                                <i class="fas fa-circle"></i> <%= p.risk_level %>
                                            </span>
                                        <% } %>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            <% }) %>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="4">
                                    <div class="empty-state">
                                        <div class="empty-icon">
                                            <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h4>No Alerts Detected</h4>
                                        <p>No medicine repetitions detected in the last 2 months</p>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        <% } %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- System Notes -->
        <div class="info-card">
            <div class="info-card-header">
                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                <h5>About the Prediction System</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card-body">
                <ul class="info-list">
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                        <span>System analyzes medicine usage patterns over the <strong>last 2 months</strong></span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        <span>
                            <span class="risk-indicator high"><i class="fas fa-circle"></i> High Risk</span>
                            6+ uses of same medicine = Possible chronic condition requiring attention
                        </span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
                        <span>
                            <span class="risk-indicator warning"><i class="fas fa-circle"></i> Warning</span>
                            4-5 uses = Potential dependency warning
                        </span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                        <span>Admin cannot modify prediction rules ‚Äì monitoring-only access for transparency</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i>
                        <span><strong>Recommended Actions:</strong> Review with attending doctors, consider patient counseling if needed</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="page-footer">
        <p>¬© 2025 Medisync Admin Panel. Connecting Care, Predicting Health.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
